	<description>
	In Space Garbage, you take the role of Elca Pitán, a space handyman who gets sent to various places within the space colony of Neo-Mexico to do repairs. Armed with gravity-defying abilities, make your way through nontraditional platforming challenges on your way to your next job... or explore the space-age Third World you live in, gossiping with people, witnessing strange events, and collecting cool hats!
	</description>
	
