	<features>
		<feature>Hundreds of nontraditional platforming challenges </feature>
		<feature>Spacious and varied space-age Third World areas to explore.</feature>
		<feature>Lots of interesting characters to meet and strange events to get mixed up in</feature>
		<feature>Multiple ways of breaking the laws of physics</feature>
		<feature>More than a few ways of breaking the law of man</feature>
		<feature>Collectable hats</feature>
